phrases: Why are you dressed that way?
Yes, all five are working hard.
Then I expect good things from their finals.
I have a bit of a selfish request.
I would like to quit tutoring as of today.
Are you aware that Nino and Itsuki got in a fight and ran away from home?
Are not you curious about why they got in a fight?
Do not you care to know what they are thinking or what is bothering them?
Oh, sorry, I should not talk like that to my employer.
Why do not you try acting like a father like once?!
You have gone and done it now.
I will not give my daughters to a man like you.
I would always gotten allowances until last year.
I should have stayed home to study.
I do not need my fortune told to know how my year's going to be.
Ever since I met those girls, I have always had...
Why do not you stop by our place?
Why did you even invite us over?
Come on, it is the new year.
I made a New Year's meal.
I think I had the wrong idea about you all.
I would heard your family was really rich.
Sorry we do not really have much.
We have to return the kimonos to our landlord, too.
Anyway, you can make yourself at home.
Are you guys sure you are all right?
Why are you sitting over there?
Come on, do not be shy.
I will give you a massage.
No, I am not really tired.
I would like to massage his legs, then.
Onii-chan's popular all of a sudden!
Mom, spring has come early for Onii-chan.
We are just thanking you for everything.
Please have some of my food, if you would like.
Why do not we play fukuwarai to get into the New Year's spirit?
There is something we would like to discuss with you.
It is too early for that!
Why do not we all go to the other room?
I do not think it bothers him at all.
We are asking him to continue teaching us without pay.
I want to do something for him.
And I do not want to depend on Father, if we can avoid it.
But what is there that we could do for him?
You were thinking the same thing, were not you?
I cannot imagine that would make Futaro-kun happy.
He is a guy, after all.
You are an actress, are not you?
You could give him a peck on the cheek.
Wh-What exactly do you think actresses do?
B-But I mean, in that case...
You have really led me on.
What are you all talking about?
Why not just do something normal and cook for him?
You are good at cooking, Nino.
Make him some snacks or something.
I was finally getting over it.
Why do not we just go tell him what is going on?
I am pretty sure it is this one.
Uesugi-san, you have cream on your face.
Let us just call that peck on the cheek a payment for your tutoring.
I did not expect that from Yotsuba.
We are not in any position to compensate you fairly right now.
Oh, you could have said so.
I am just doing it because I want to.
Do not worry about paying me.
You can just give me a cut when you make it big.
But I want it in writing!
Five thousand yen per person per day of tutoring!
And I will collect, right down to the last yen!
Right, that is how he is.
And all five of you are here right now.
Let us get cracking on the winter homework!
We have all done our homework already.
Well, let us just make it a regular study session, then.
I am going to go home so I do not get in the way.
Can you help me with this bit?
Provide examples of words ending with -ish?
-ish is a suffix that means approximately, or kind of.
There is also peckish, but that is...
Let her sleep for a while.
Ichika's been working even more than before.
She is paying our bills and expenses.
It is all thanks to Ichika that we get to have you here to teach us.
But what is the point if she cannot focus on studying?
Why do not we work, too?
Do you have any work experience?
Will you have time to both study and work?
All of you are struggling to even pass.
I will work as a tutor, like you do.
I will teach as I study.
That way, I can improve my academics, too.
It is two birds with one stone.
I would feel sorry for your students.
How about working at a supermarket, then?
I want to try working at a maid cafe.
You would probably be a dominatrix, right, Nino?
What is that supposed to mean?
Nino would work in food service, right?
If I had to choose, sure.
It is always been your dream to open your own shop.
First I have heard of it.
It is just a silly idea I had as a kid.
Do not take it too seriously.
I know a good cake shop.
I have worked several jobs so far,
but they all took some commitment.
Please stop taking your clothes off in your sleep!
Teach in any subject you are comfortable
Fun home tutoring (Minimum two days per week, one shift each!)
It is been a while, Itsuki-kun.
What do you think of my pie?
It is just like yours, boss!
I should not be talking trash about Miku.
Looks like it will be a while before I can let you in the kitchen.
We are closing at noon today.
We are renting the shop out for a movie shoot.
You could have told me sooner.
Looking forward to working with you today.
the fans will be coming in droves to visit the site.
We will have a pick with our business name in the cakes that will be on the screen.
I wish I had his insatiable hunger.
I look forward to working with you.
I have always wanted to try this cake shop.
They say if you get one, you die.
I am too dumb to know what you are talking about.
Let us just have some cake!
Why would you take up embarrassing work?
I am trying not to tell the others,
but we are running out of savings.
I mean, it turns out food and power is a lot more expensive than I thought.
So I decided to accept any work I can find.
I have to be strong for the girls.
So do not try to stop me.
I am not going to dismiss your efforts.
And I am grateful to you for giving me an opportunity to continue tutoring.
But I am sure you could do better.
Is not this job still pretty unprofitable for how much it ties you down?
Nakano-san, we are ready to start rolling.
That one was good, but why do not we try another take?
I wish the others could see her being so ditzy.
I hope you do not mind us using this pie for one more take.
It is the dud that I made!
You do not have anything to hide.
These things are only cool when done in secret.
Are you done with your script?
I memorized the whole thing already.
Why cannot you use that skill for studying?
The curse kills me in the first part, so I do not have that many lines.
Is the cake here all right?
If I am being kind, it was unique.
If I am being brutal, it was like Miku's home cooking.
It is true that you surprised me, though.
Y-You are kind of growing into your job as an actress.
She almost had me saying something smug to her.
Man, I am amazed you can hide your embarrassment in front of so many people.
I really wish the others could see you.
I hate that I am even acting in this moment...
But I could not let him see my face right now.
The most efficient way of carrying this load is...
Why did you call me out at this hour?
They are having a sale today.
And you should be able to carry that yourself.
Miku asked me to buy these.
You are pretty dense for someone who is so smart.
Can you hold this for a sec?
Maybe I have not gotten over Kintaro-kun yet.
It does not make sense otherwise.
There is no way this guy's my prince!
Bring us every kind of sandwich you have.
You are amenable and quick to understand, Itsuki-kun.
I believe that is what is meant when one is called intelligent.
That was him at the hospital back then.
I will turn a blind eye to the mistake you girls have made.
Come back home with the others immediately.
Does that include him as well?
He is an outsider in every sense.
What did you do to Dad?
He is far too involved in this to call him an outsider.
I will allow Uesugi-kun back into the home,
and ask him to continue tutoring.
But he will be working alongside a professional tutor.
He will be acting as her support.
But we are all working so hard.
Do you even suppose, if Uesugi-kun was brought back in as your tutor as before,
that Yotsuba-kun could earn a passing grade?
From what I have seen of her grades in the second term, I have very little hope.
You will only make things worse if you go.
We will have a better chance with two tutors.
Uesugi-san and the five of us can do it.
I want the six of us to pull it off.
We will not make the same mistake again.
I would rather not say this out loud,
but I have made an arrangement with an acquaintance
who is a board member at a high school that would allow you to enroll as third-years.
If you fail on the next exam, I will have you transfer to that school.
If you insist on doing things your way, the responsibility is all yours.
Then I will finalize the arrangements.
We will accept the condition that we transfer schools if we do not make it.
I am sorry I am not an amenable, understanding, intelligent child.
It seems that the duty of a parent is to hear the selfish demands of their children.
And it is also the duty of a parent to scold their selfishness.
